## 1_variables.med
## Declaring and printing variables of different types

Admission <: :> [:
    Organ    age      =: 25 |
    Flow     weight   =: 72.5 |
    Diabetes height   =: 1.75 |
    Cell     initial  =: 'M' |
    Sealed Organ MAX_DOSE =: 500 |

    Observe <: "Age     : %d\n", age :> |
    Observe <: "Weight  : %f kg\n", weight :> |
    Observe <: "Height  : %f m\n", height :> |
    Observe <: "Initial : %c\n", initial :> |
    Observe <: "Max Dose: %d mg\n", MAX_DOSE :> |
:]
